.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5236ce7deb3873fd85284636228c3f96ed238bb8","tid":236692,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:18:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁都食唔出？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n個皮已經好大分別喇喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc47f099ce4fb3c195c99fea319c69dfda577322","tid":236692,"uid":20815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:19:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>餃就煎餃<br />\n湯就雲吞</blockquote><br />\n正解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c212eac0c5ec22a79102c93f9179f1b4cdbf560","tid":236692,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:20:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>蝦雲吞</blockquote><br />\n諗起有間專賣大蝦雲吞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n每個雲吞都塞幾隻蝦入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似係尖沙嘴 唔記得咩名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a1b8a765cc82e1b60cf2230b161ce7478662427","tid":236692,"uid":36691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-10T02:20:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有咩分別<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n皮厚度雲吞薄d滑d，有梘水味<br />\n饀料雲吞多數蝦肉，餃就菜肉<br />\nbtw,蒸煎就餃<br />\n水煮就雲吞"},{"pid":"e7f7c87b401b5b2