0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T10:34:48.000Z","msg":"雖然投左正評<br />\n但話水餃唔好食既人一定冇食過好好食既水餃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好食既水餃皮唔可以太薄<br />\n咬落去塊皮要有彈牙既感覺<br />\n只要餡料夠新鮮 就算只係菜同豬肉都可以做到好出色 鮮味多汁<br />\n<br />\n可惜係香港搵唔到咁高汁既水餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食過最好食既餃子係北京d巷仔小店到<br />\n講番起都好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"defcedf86d9c6f62dadc254c73e7a2300309ad99","tid":236692,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T11:32:28.000Z","msg":"水餃無論餡同皮都差過雲吞太多, 根本無得比! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c841b1829506821302b1a42529a9940900150c1","tid":236692,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T13:32:07.000Z","msg":"一般黎講就雲吞<br />\n但一講到韭菜餃就好難比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e857cb0f8d63c959354864541bcbd51ba9432623","tid":236692,"uid":11844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-12T14:45:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>雖然投左正評<br />\n但話水餃唔好食既人一定冇食過好好食既水餃囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好食既水餃皮唔可以太薄<br />\n咬落去塊皮要有彈牙既感覺<br />\n只要餡料夠新鮮 就算只係菜同豬肉都可以做到好出色 鮮味多汁<br />\n<br />\n可惜係香港搵唔到咁高汁既水餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食過最好食既餃子係北京d巷仔小店到<br />\n講番起都好懷念<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nAgger<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港真係食唔到好食嘅水餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有次去個frd屋企<br />\n佢阿爸阿媽係北京人落黎<br />\n<br />\n煮個餐水餃真係食唔停口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"beb1a01340ff549bfe2c758cd5f7dbe92f174ed0","tid":236692,"uid":12536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T04:39:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>水餃好食咁多 唔係掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你應該未食過真正既雲吞</blockquote><br />\n我鐘意食韮菜餃 而身邊人個個都鐘意雲吞 但我好討厭陣梘水味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n梘水皮同蝦兩樣都唔like<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幫水餃拉票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48c066fe1ad2bd5faef3146f6fca18a165ed1abd","tid":236692,"uid":92276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-13T05:31:46.000Z","msg":"好食嘅水餃難揾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大部份都皮過厚唔合我口味"},{"pid":"1e72fde6178ee389407018ff18b12b55334740ec","tid":236692,"uid":48473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:45:36.000Z","msg":"勁中意食上海菜肉雲吞"},{"pid":"82b5ec7097fdab3130291810352f46e74deaf2d4","tid":236692,"uid":27221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:57:46.000Z","msg":"鳳城水餃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b408f9fd375186ec19069daeca73f8f1f29c4fb7","tid":236692,"uid":40206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:01:50.000Z","msg":"鳳城水餃冇得輸啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5262814937edd29b10324951eeb67d6b6d900c","tid":236692,"uid":1749,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"鍋貼la"},{